{
  "stem": "6719.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Um, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Do you want me to start from the beginning?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we got out of the train.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was screaming and shouting down the end.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had people that we saw that were running around in striped uniforms that I knew already from-- this I remember from-- from Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's for sure.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "With their full uniform, you know, their jacket and their pants and, uh, and, uh, and their-- their beret.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, uh, a lot of SS with dogs, and with-- with rifles and with the pistols, and all that kind of horse manure.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And, uh, we lined up, uh, the women to the left, and with the children, and the men, all men, to the right.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then we went through the routine of the selection, where the physician-- if I can use-- I shouldn't use that word because he was just a butcher-- was standing there.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And when I came up and he asked me what, uh, what is your-- I was 18 years old.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "What's your profession?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I'm a tailor.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Go-- pointed to the right, OK?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And as I say, there was only-- there were only 26 people in total.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I don't know how many women.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I don't know how many we were, if we were 15 or 20 guys, or-- or-- or 16 guys that went.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I don't remember that anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we marched into Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so the first thing that I saw down there in Auschwitz was, uh, the sign, which is famous, 'Arbeit Macht Frei.' And I don't think that I have to translate that.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, uh, so we marched in, and then I-- I-- I saw a sight that-- that-- stays with me until today.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Gee, ?] it was-- it was early in the morning.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
